Summary I'm a 27 year old beard man entrepreneur with a heart beating for (web) designed applications and advertising. Back in the days, at the age of 14, I started (web)designing and coding several websites. At the age of 15 I became co-owner of the biggest dutch website in a certain niche (we had over 10.000 unique visitors á day!). From there on I started to build websites for small company's that were located in and around Tilburg. Now (10+ years later) I have build over 100 website's for small, medium and big company's across the whole nation. My interest in design and development will never expire.  

I like to believe that: 
- I'm a good (project) Manager; 
- I'm a decent Teamplayer; 
- I'm a Creative thinker; 
- I'm great at coming up with new concepts/idea's; 
- I'm great at motivating people to achieve their goals. 

Over the years I also had some experience with certain tools, program's and coding languages.  
- I sleep in Adobe Photoshop; 
- I draw in Adobe Illustrator; 
- I often create cool documents with Adobe Indesign; 
- I know every syntax of xHTML / HTML5; 
- I write stylesheets blindly with CSS / CSS3; 
- I can create some fancy functionalities in PHP; 
- I animate my idea's with Javascript; 
- I can also store, retrieve, calculate data in Mysql. 

Enough about me, let's talk about you.  
